    <title type="display">Lewis &amp; Clark Regional Water System Expansion Feasibility Study Act</title>
    <title type="short" as="introduced">Lewis &amp; Clark Regional Water System Expansion Feasibility Study Act</title>
    <title type="official" as="introduced">A bill to require the Secretary of the Interior to conduct a study to determine the feasibility of constructing a project to supply municipal, rural, and industrial water to expand the capacity and reach of the Lewis and Clark Rural Water System, Inc. (doing business as "Lewis &amp; Clark Regional Water System"), in the States of Iowa, Minnesota, and South Dakota.</title>
  </titles>
